videos.description: Devonte Green knocks down back-to-back 3-pointers to increase Indiana's lead over Penn State.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Green buries back-to-back 3s to cap Indiana's 11-0 run) 2020/2/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: Green buries back-to-back 3s to cap Indiana's 11-0 run

videos.description: Lamar Stevens drives through traffic and gets the layup to drop to put Penn State ahead.
videos.headline: Stevens finishes through contact

videos.description: Trayce Jackson-Davis goes head-to-head with Lamar Stevens and steps by him with ease for the slam.

videos.description: On the 35th anniversary of Bobby Knight throwing his chair, Archie Miller emulates his anger on a clipboard after Indiana misses free throws down the stretch.
